tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE orders (
  order_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  product_id INT,
  quantity INT,
  total_price DECIMAL(10, 2),
  order_date TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE orders (
  order_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  product_id INT,
  quantity_ordered INT,
  order_date TIMESTAMP,
  FOREIGN KEY (product_id) REFERENCES products(product_id)
);

CREATE TABLE products (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    name VARCHAR(255),
    price DECIMAL(10, 2),
    quantity INT,
    category VARCHAR(50)
);

CREATE TABLE inventory (
    product_id INT,
    warehouse_id INT,
    quantity INT,
    PRIMARY KEY (product_id, warehouse_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (product_id) REFERENCES products(id),
    FOREIGN KEY (warehouse_id) REFERENCES warehouses(id)
);

CREATE TABLE orders (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    product_id INT,
    quantity INT,
    status VARCHAR(50),
    order_date DATE,
    FOREIGN KEY (product_id) REFERENCES products(id)
);
